Package: pscreen-cli
Version: 2.0.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 18.0.0), npm
Maintainer: PScreen Team <pscreen@example.com>
Description: Professional Playwright Screenshot CLI Tool
 Advanced CLI tool for taking screenshots of web pages using Playwright.
 Features include full-page screenshots, viewport capture, web server interface,
 automatic port management, external IP detection, and batch processing support.
 .
 Version 2.0.1 includes improved port conflict resolution and automatic fallback
 to available ports when the specified port is in use.
